buaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/06\/divorce-triple-talaq\/","url_meta":{"origin":33902,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Divorce: Triple talaq in the time of the Prophet, Abu Bakr, and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: Triple divorce in the time of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, Abu Bakr, and two years of the Caliphate of Umar was considered to be only one revocable divorce. Umar ibn al-Khattab said, \u201cVerily, the people have become hasty in a matter\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33889,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/07\/umar-talaq-triple-divorce\/","url_meta":{"origin":33902,"position":1},"title":"Umar on Talaq: The Caliph punishes men who triple divorce","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 7, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: Whenever a man was brought to Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, who had divorced his wife three times in one sitting, he would flog his back. Source: Sharh\u0323 Ma\u02bba\u0304ni\u0304 al-\u0100tha\u0304r 4488 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25668,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.